Package io.outofprintmagazine.nlp.pipeline

Class OOPAnnotations

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.outofprintmagazine.nlp.pipeline.OOPAnnotations
  • public class OOPAnnotations
extends Object

    Defines OOP custom annotations.

    Conventionally, custom annotators return ONLY ONE annotation type.

    OOP annotations adopt the annotation conventions from Core Nlp: getType()

    Author:
    Ram Sadasiv
